{"TopicId":208275,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"I am having trouble with this dreamchaser-like craft.","CreatedByName":"BekfastDerp13","CreatedById":214450,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-21T14:09:12Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"BekfastDerp13","CreatedById":214450,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-21T14:09:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen I start out launching, the rocket is fine. Whenever I start the gravity turn, it flips! Can you help me solve this problem?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is a column of reaction wheels inside the rocket, slightly offset to the back (west direction, since this spacecraft faces east). I did that to keep the center of mass in the middle.\u003Cimg alt=\u0022v2gA9VQ.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022193.23\u0022 height=\u0022970\u0022 width=\u0022502\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/v2gA9VQ.png\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis probably should be moved, I forgot to add.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BekfastDerp13","CreatedById":214450,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-21T14:26:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNever mind, I got it to work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-21T19:13:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe usual causes are too much drag at the front of the craft and/or not enough control authority. With the wing parts you have on that uppermost stage, I suspect it was drag and airflow. For the benefit of others, how did you solve it?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BekfastDerp13","CreatedById":214450,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-21T20:00:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224135679\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022208275\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221653160423\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n45 minutes ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe usual causes are too much drag at the front of the craft and/or not enough control authority. With the wing parts you have on that uppermost stage, I suspect if was drag and airflow. For the benefit of others, how did you solve it?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni put a crappy fairing around it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncould this thread be closed or something please?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-21T20:29:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224135691\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022208275\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221653163238\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022214450\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022BekfastDerp13\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, BekfastDerp13 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni put a crappy fairing around it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA prettier solution would be to put larger wings on the back.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-21T21:07:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224135691\